    public class FileSpec

    The FileSpec class contains information enabling access to a file resident in the QRDA file repository defined in the QRDA_HOME/qrda filespace. A FileSpec object is used primarily as a display object for displaying information about a file in a UI. The FileSpec class is also the base class for the TestCase class, used by the validation process in conjunction with a ValidationSuite instance.
